{"tid":2050213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外電：有跨國企業擬將資金管理部分由香港移往新加坡等國","createTime":"2020-06-04T03:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T04:09:38.000Z","uid":21470,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0097b1ad488f7e563f9e47808abffd0a7303a88d","tid":2050213,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:48:28.000Z","msg":"外電：有跨國企業擬將部分業務由香港移往新加坡等國<br />\n04.06.2020 10:48<br />\n<br />\n外電引述資深銀行家指，由於憂慮美國會取消香港特殊待遇，部份跨國企業考慮將部份財資管理業務，包括現金管理及外匯買賣，由香港移往新加坡、馬來西亞、泰國和越南等國，但沒有確實時間表。有銀行人士指，如果美國取消香港的特殊待遇，香港商品就會像中國商品一樣被美國加徵關稅，貿易流動將受到衝擊。香港對美國進口商品也會面臨風險，因此跨國企業正考慮先將部份資金業務移出香港，再逐步擴大規模，當中包括一間在亞洲各地經營數百間連鎖店的美國主要零售商，希望將部份業務轉到新加坡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1299151&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1299151%26csid%3D261_341&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=d4eafa23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1299151&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"07ce9fed8358672688ffc154ba5400984aeb52ef","tid":2050213,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:49:13.000Z","msg":"港共: 有基本法保障  沒事兒"},{"pid":"c19fac8d51bfe84469cd60a9bcdfa0991bb574d6","tid":2050213,"uid":68080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:50:12.000Z","msg":"why not all<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bfbc7cdc3a100221667368fd5f040950db43944","tid":2050213,"uid":159913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:50:35.000Z","msg":"港共：外資撤離因不了解一國兩制"},{"pid":"504b157cfb5c3ff8c4ae5fe5a776c9229fb5849b","tid":2050213,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:51:22.000Z","msg":"而家唔制裁, 只係俾時間堆美資走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree